# Absolo Cloud — CODEOWNERS
#
# Path-based ownership. PRs touching these paths require approval from the
# listed owners. Sensitive paths (iam, billing, security, host-agent,
# edge-proxy) require 2 approvals (configured in branch protection).
#
# This file will be populated with real GitHub usernames as engineers join.
# Until then it acts as a placeholder so paths are documented.

# default
